<p />
<p />
<h2 class="twikinetRoundedAttachments"><span class="twikinetHeader"><a name="ObjectMethod_forceAuthentication"></a> <a href="/bin/view/TWiki/ObjectMethod" class="twikiLink">ObjectMethod</a> <strong>forceAuthentication</strong> <tt>() -&gt; boolean</tt> </span></h2>
<p />
method called when authentication is required - redirects to (...|view)auth
Triggered on auth fail
<p />
<p />
<p />
<h2 class="twikinetRoundedAttachments"><span class="twikinetHeader"><a name="ObjectMethod_loginUrl_loginUrl"></a> <a href="/bin/view/TWiki/ObjectMethod" class="twikiLink">ObjectMethod</a> <strong>loginUrl</strong> <tt>() -&gt; $loginUrl</tt> </span></h2>
