<h2 class="twikinetRoundedAttachments"><span class="twikinetHeader"><a name="ObjectMethod_getUser_authUser"></a> <a href="/bin/view/TWiki/ObjectMethod" class="twikiLink">ObjectMethod</a> <strong>getUser</strong> <tt>() -&gt; $authUser</tt> </span></h2>
